        {
          "username": "Pasquale",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "103141939768674419205",
          "user_review_count": 11,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2c5ppjt4yVnOlEwkqRl-oNgYMPTnGZ5T2pTWr5Im-MedW_xeb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "After using big box pharmacies for years with some inconsistencies, I decided to switch to a privately owned pharmacy. I found ProHealth Pharmacy and could not be happier! The gentleman Alex, who I assume is if not the owner the main pharmacist is extremely friendly and attentive as well as patient and kind. Without me even having to call, I've received my prescriptions within an hour of them being called in because they offer free delivery service. I'm assuming that that free delivery service is location sensitive if you know what I mean. Overall if I can give them six stars I would!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SNWRrWkJVbFZ3VUZKdGNrbFFjblpTU0ZCVVlYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmR5dkZBUlVwUFJtcklQcnZSSFBUYXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "4 weeks ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-26T22:29:48+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Sabena Singh",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "116607482068877925357",
          "user_review_count": 321,
          "user_photo_count": 4310,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtvV49w-SIFiCsWT_TIk1I8iiueF69YUYUvWxyOA_brx8Cowg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Independent pharmacies like Prohealth on Second Avenue are a treasure. While stocking up on medical needs, they also have diversions like lotions, potions, candles, pretty cards, diffusers and other olfactory and skin care delights. After all the browsing and shopping, one has to pay. But temptation lurks at the checkout - chocolate bars! These bars with assorted inclusions are from Los Angeles. While a tad expensive these are worth every penny and are tasty. I have to have self control not to buy one and occasionally buy a miniature bar.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paWlVIZENTRWhZYm1ka01qSnROSEJWVGsweVFYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjZZUHdCSEhYbmdkMjJtNHBVTk0yQXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "images": [
            {
              "thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Lqmp1qSxmN7VMLekN8lfna3TZ6CbsBkWfNIUwSQJePssrWKu1fPxhndkBK9umzqpF2BnPzyRpa7Xa-pHKektYtR7zxuLWYKIw26WOfAkSIajdMe_Ki7PaJMMLu_59N_wC8XIC-EugXe0x=k-no"
            }
          ],
          "date": "8 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-10-25T01:36:34+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Keith Friedman",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "103646623555472751935",
          "user_review_count": 12,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRsfnetfdluIA0pCy9rek5fm_DUIF6z3-3zPm95WZLEJ-dKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I don't write many reviews -- and I certainly don't write many five star reviews! But ProHealth really deserves it.\n\nI should probably start by saying that I generally prefer mom-and-pop businesses to chains. Before I started going to ProHealth, I went to a local Duane Reade. My only regret is that I didn't know about this place sooner! Alex, who owns ProHealth, not only knows his stuff: he and the other staff members genuinely care about customers. I'm sure I don't have to tell you how rare that is these days. They are always helpful and sometimes they fill a prescription before I even call it in! I also appreciate their location.\n\nAll in all, I would highly recommend ProHealth if you need a good pharmacy.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oeWNUSkdVV0pwTnkxRVNHNHRRekpyYVU1d1NVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmhycTJGUWJpNy1ESG4tQzJraU5wSUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "9 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-08-30T23:49:19+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Timothy McManus",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "116262982666648747706",
          "user_review_count": 12,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVClb2dwPCWmIccsnnEuMo6zENFKjctzyXFiMtuD5h3LAp7PPZ_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Best pharmacy in the city. I\u2019m kind of worried to give this review bc I want to keep it a secret but it\u2019s the best. So fast and super helpful.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBeVNuRTROakpCVVdaUldXOVlWV1JGVTFWTGRuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlAySnE4NjJBUWZRWW9YVWRFU1VLdnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "5 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-01-12T21:56:52+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Creative Solutions",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "105084334234960056369",
          "user_review_count": 26,
          "user_photo_count": 49,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJLfrfPkMPncZj49enZVp8zCai-rcnuy7SE4nO-IFptrqCRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I recently reached out to ProHealth Pharmacy at the direction of my medical provider, who has worked with other clients who have successfully filed the same prescription there in the past. I made the call politely , explaining that I was reaching out at the behest of my practitioner and then provided the name of my medication.\n\nThe male who answered the phone mumbled something that I believe was a \"no\" and then abruptly hung up. I was left feeling dismissed and disrespected. It's quite something to realize that this pharmacy has enough clients to disregard potential new patients in need of assistance.\n\nAs a store that markets itself as family owned and neighborhood friendly, I would caution anyone seeking compassionate care or respectful service. This business clearly lacks both. Avoid\nProHealth Pharmacy at all costs unless you don't mind experiencing poor customer service when reaching out for something as important as your monthly maintenance.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VNN1c1LWEydzgteTBBRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEM7W5-a2w8-y0AE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a year ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-05-16T19:33:46+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Morgan Brown",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "117616421637332639073",
          "user_review_count": 15,
          "user_photo_count": 14,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpQj2GTMdPREEL0kcTzzkX0mZY2EsPe5Bpwb_nJpQFqRot0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Amazingly helpful staff who go above and beyond for you. They make sure that your insurance info is correct so that no fees come out of your pocket, they are swift and knowledgeable with any and all questions, and are patient and kind to their customers. They also have medications in stock that are hard to find elsewhere. My newest favorite pharmacy. Thank you so much.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUR3dDZ1dEpnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgMDwt6utJg%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a year ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-03-28T23:24:50+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Eileen Fitzgerald",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "102512811616654277557",
          "user_review_count": 13,
          "user_photo_count": 2,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWKHYBdxeM_KTSxluvRu94ee3XYcLu5kq6mwKAhY4d2MIj0lrd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I\u2019ve been going here for at least 20 years and have always enjoyed the product selection, the ambiance (an odd description for a pharmacy, but appropriate for this one) and the lovely and patience of the staff. It reminds me of pharmacies I\u2019ve been to in Europe. They sell a lot of homeopathic and obscure supplements and salves, natural beauty products, beautifully smelling soaps and candles, in addition to hair products and ornaments you wouldn\u2019t find in a big box CVS or Walgreens. The lighting is lovely, there\u2019s no fluorescent lights or obnoxious background music, and seems to be designed to bring the customers anxiety level down. I wish there were more in the city; I find it torture to go to the bigger pharmacies when I have Pro Health as an option. In addition, they also sell the more mainstream over the counter products.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuajRuNFRnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDnj4n4Tg%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a year ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2024-10-11T13:05:56+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "lauren m",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "112152224876934270333",
          "user_review_count": 6,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJX3fPg1iwS5ho8HSqfRyLVhQb4K8L48cVR73d20Rx6LdPkCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Don't normally leave reviews but wanted to thank Dr. Alex and his team for the great service I received over the holidays. Was worried about getting my PCR results back in time for my flight to Canada ...found this place online and walked in ...was seen within 20 min and received my results an hour later. There were a few clerical issues with the PDF I received, I called back and within 10 min everything was rectified.\n\nYes, the test is pricey but if you are looking for guaranteed results in a short time frame this is the place to go! No issues boarding my flight!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNtd2JqbTVRRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d7b659226bd65d0!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICmwbjm5QE%7C%7C?hl=en",
